                      >
                        Jeudi
                      </td>
                      <td
                        class="text-sm bg-green-100 border-green-200 text-gray-900 font-light px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap"
                      >
                        10h à 12h
                      </td>
                      <td
                        class="text-sm bg-green-100 border-green-200 text-gray-900 font-light px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap"
                      >
                        10h à 12h
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="border">
                      <td
                        class="text-sm text-gray-900 font-medium px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap"
                      >
